Tips for installation from zero (from a fresh ubuntu platform)

** Install some packages:
gnuplot
libf2c2-dev
libqhull-dev
liblapack-dev
freeglut3-dev
libann-dev
doxygen

** Compile
make

** Test
cd test/array;  ./x.exe
cd test/soc;    ./x.exe

** Read
cd doc/soc_doc;  firefox index.html
acroread doc/guides/soc_guide.pdf
